.claude/
# Ref: SRS 18.7 - real secrets never committed. .env.production lives only
# on the server; the .example template (placeholders, no real values) is
# fine to commit and is explicitly un-ignored below.
.env*
!.env.production.example

# Maven build output - the backend image compiles this from source inside
# Docker, so compiled classes and the packaged jar never belong in the repo.
target/

# Locally uploaded/generated files (profile photos, lesson resources, issued
# certificates, report exports). These live in a Docker volume in dev and in
# object storage in staging/prod - never in git.
uploads/
# ...but not the frontend route that proxies to them - that's source code.
!frontend/src/app/api/uploads/
